    dc:description "FIGURES 1–8. Culama species, adults. Figs 1–2. C. australis. 1. ♂, Victoria (CAK). 2. ♀, New South Wales (ANIC). Figs 3–4. C. anthracica sp. nov., Victoria. 3. ♂ (holotype, ANIC). 4. ♀ (paratype, CAK). Fig. 5. C. crepera, ♀, Western Australia (ANIC). Fig. 6. C. dasythrix, ♂, Western Australia (ANIC). Figs 7–8. C. suffusca sp. nov., Victoria. 7. ♂ (holotype, ANIC). 8. ♀ (paratype, CAK)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5254711/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5254715>
    dc:description "FIGURES 24–31. Cossinae, adults. Figs 24–25. Macrocyttara expressa. Queensland. 24. ♂ (ANIC). 25. ♀ (ANIC). Figs 26–27. M. pamphaea. Queensland. 26. ♂, South Australia (ANIC). 27. ♀, New South Wales (ANIC). Figs 28–29. Zyganisus fulvicollis, Victoria. 28. ♂ (CAK). 29. ♀ (CDH). 28. ♂, Victoria (holotype, ANIC). 29. ♀, Victoria (paratype, MVM). Figs 30–31. Z. caliginosus, 30–33. ♂ (New South Wales, CAK). 31. ♀ (Victoria, CDH)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5254715/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5254717>
    dc:description "FIGURES 32–39. Zyganisus species, adults. Fig. 32. Z. caliginosus, Victoria, ♂ (CAK). 33–35. Z. cadigalorum sp. nov., New South Wales (ANIC). 33. ♂ (paratype). 34. ♂ (holotype). 35. ♀ (paratype). Figs 36–38. Z. propedia sp. nov., paratypes. 36. ♂ (Victoria, CAK). 37. ♀ (Victoria, MVM). 38. ♀ (Western Australia, ANIC). Fig. 39. Z. acalanthis sp. nov., ♂, holotype, Western Australia (ANIC)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5254717/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5254721>
    dc:description "FIGURES 46–51. Cossinae species, male genitalia. Fig. 46. Culama alpina sp. nov. (GP AK606, CAK). Figs 47–48. C. glauca sp. nov. 47. (GP AK640, ANIC). 48. (GP AK688, ANIC). Fig. 49. Macrocyttara pamphaea (GP AK692, ANIC). Fig. 50. Zyganisus fulvicollis (GP AK628, CAK). Fig. 51. Z. caliginosus (GP AK689, CAK)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5254721/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5254729>
    dc:description "FIGURES 68–79. Zyganisus species, details of male genitalia. Figs 68–73. Juxta and transtilla. Fig. 68. Z. fulvicollis (GP AK628, ANIC). Fig. 69. Z. caliginosus (GP AK689, CAK). Figs 70–71. Z. cadigalorum sp. nov. 70. GP AK706 (AMS). 71. GP AK712 (AMS). Fig. 72. Z. propedia sp. nov.(GP AK629, ANIC). Fig. 73. Z. acalanthis sp. nov. (GP AK642, ANIC). Figs 74–79. Phalli. Fig. 74. Z. fulvicollis (GP AK628, ANIC). Fig. 75. Z. caliginosus (GP AK689, CAK). Figs 76–77. Z. cadigalorum sp. nov. 76. GP AK706 (AMS). 77. GP AK712 (AMS). Fig. 78. Z. propedia sp. nov. (GP AK629, ANIC). Fig. 79. Z. acalanthis sp. nov.(GP AK642, ANIC)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5254729/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5254731>
    dc:description "FIGURES 80–83. Cossinae species, female genitalia (total, upper panel, and ostium, lower panel). Fig. 80. Culama australis (GP 714, CAK). Fig. 81. C. suffusca sp. nov. (GP AK633, CAK). Fig. 82. C. alpina sp. nov. (GP AK619, ANIC). Fig. 83. Zyganisus fulvicollis (GP AK632, CAK)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5254731/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5254757>
    dc:description "FIGURES 167–172. Distribution Maps, Cossinae. 167. Macrocyttara expressa (), M. pamphaea (⊖). 168. Zyganisus fulvicollis sp. nov. 169. Z. caliginosus. 170. Z. propedia. 171. Z. acalanthis sp. nov. (), Z. cadigalorum (⊖). 172. Cossodes lyonetii." ;
